29-2502.Omitted.

SourceLaws 2015, LB268, ยง 23;Referendum 2016, No. 426.Note:Section 29-2502, newly enacted by Laws 2015, LB 268, section 23, and assigned by the Revisor of Statutes to section 29-2502, has been omitted because of the vote on the referendum at the November 2016 general election.
